{"tid":2404694,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"基於一國一制原制 香港電台不再專播BBC","createTime":"2021-02-12T01:14:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-12T06:08:16.000Z","uid":21470,"like":20,"dislike":317,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"daa24af19101ac2dc27ab0690257144e1a3575e8","tid":2404694,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T01:14:40.000Z","msg":"港台不再轉播BBC世界新聞頻道及「BBC時事一週」<br />\n<br />\n香港電台發言人表示，根據國家廣播電視總局不允許BBC世界新聞台繼續在中國境內落地，對其新一年度落地申請不予受理，香港電台今晚11時開始，不再轉播BBC世界新聞頻道及「BBC時事一週」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1575404-20210212.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1575404-20210212.htm&d=fMmZVRBh8JxXvfCabRklGQ1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=b9eedf88\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1575404-20210212.htm&h=0ece55b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1575404-20210212.htm</a>"},{"pid":"e7969fc817a01013a09f3c5bac3010cc5c2cd6f7","tid":2404694,"uid":191815,"like":148,"dislike":3,"score":145,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T01:20:30.000Z","msg":"一國兩制喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63ef3a99a0c3400a69939d3712984b02663b0e65","tid":2404694,"uid":308251,"like":14,"dislike":4,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T01:22:22.000Z","msg":"香港電台<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a248a958dacb8ead32a57613de9c6ea65b9893f9","tid":2404694,"uid":76471,"like":58,"dislike":2,"score":56,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T01:27:02.000Z","msg":"回歸咗超過20年，依家先來ban<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26022c5e5b6db48f06df461a5fc9979960040b2c","tid":2404694,"uid":20262,"like":54,"dislike":2,"score":52,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T01:27:06.000Z","msg":"咁係咪代表可以解散廣管局"},{"pid":"6a9e608f8292