9","tid":2404694,"uid":225130,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"edcdb484bdc425ae151b77e4c767b1d21c4ace31","tid":2404694,"uid":229777,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"cad9cb3b66479ccb969f00a1fec2bdb846dfff7b","tid":2404694,"uid":225130,"like":61,"dislike":3,"score":58,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T01:29:23.000Z","msg":"咁點解貨物又寫made in UK<br />\nmade in china啦屌你<br />\n公務員跟大陸payscale"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T01:36:25.000Z","msg":"英國變咗中國一部份？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T01:37:29.000Z","msg":"hk 打錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T01:37:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b29361f47f99e56001afc7c29baa54cfdcc0e09","tid":2404694,"uid":33336,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"e7969fc817a01013a09f3c5bac3010cc5c2cd6f7","tid":2404694,"uid":191815,"like":148,"dislike":3,"score":145,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T01:20:30.000Z","msg":"一國兩制喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T01:38:12.000Z","msg":"藍絲：一國大過兩制<br />\n<br />\n我：🤯"},{"pid":"5302c82fad8573507067a3d570437d3a1cd8f053","tid":2404694,"uid":300782,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T01:40:19.000Z","msg":"半夜，當城市已不再熱鬧，睡在床上，但並非想進睡；扭着那短波收音機，追蹤着那些「被禁」之聲，聽聽它們的立場。二十多年來，我不時也在夜間這樣做。<br />\n<br />\n懷疑過，年輕一代可能從未收聽過短波或中波的廣播，對他們來說，或許連正常的FM、AM的電台也沒有聽。網絡就是他們的一切。以往聽短波，BBC及美國之音就是最大的「敵對」陣營，這英美為首的短波戰，在冷戰時最厲害，在歐洲，用東歐各國語言、俄語不斷灌輸西方的價值觀，在亞洲，用北京語、廣東話、越南話、緬甸語等宣傳同一理念。<br />\n<br />\n一開始擺到明就是反共的，所以中共恨之入骨。若果有「追蹤」過美國之音的波頻，就知道當中的搞笑事。美國之音每晚發放廣播時，中國政府便會派人干擾它，一知道波頻位置，就會在同一波段播打鑼打鼓的《迎春曲》，試圖蓋過他們一方的廣播；於是美國之音一路「走」，《迎春曲》一路「追」！我認為這是世間上最笨的干擾行動，因為往往人們扭到《迎春曲》，就知道美國之音在附近，反而幫助了大家！<br />\n<br />\n後來，中共又出了另一招，在美國之音附近播放中國之音打對台；不過又是很笨，因為收得短波的人，本身就不想聽官方台啦！現在世界變了，美國剛宣布美國之音將結束對華廣播，令很多人也意想不到。加上停播日期竟然是今年的10月1日，中國國慶日；是有心還是無意？是美國送給中國政府的一份大禮嗎？<br />\n<br />\n雲海"},{"pid":"bd54253d030593493e9c323234cd3da6a72cb006","tid":2404694,"uid":363016,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T01:40:27.000Z","msg":"中國不可以自由訪問國際互聯網<br />\n香港幾時跟？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加速到了癲狂地步"},{"pid":"75747e6977266cdb827ef6e9be6c21e3382455cb","tid":2404694,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T01:45:50.000Z","msg":"國際笑話"},{"pid":"ecdf2b87119b7c5b1e44f1429b4c984c5a3d1a09","tid":2404694,"uid":198841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T01:46:48.000Z","msg":"班工會唔撚出聲?"},{"pid":"727f020a257dca418acfe7d75d274c033a32ed22","tid":2404694,"uid":232185,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"ecdf2b87119b7c5b1e44f1429b4c984c5a3d1a09","tid":2404694,"uid":198841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T01:46:48.000Z","msg":"班工會唔撚出聲?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T01:48:59.000Z","msg":"幾個鐘前嘅事你想點出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c20c8a5bb195a69d164ef19d4f31b04cf65378a","tid":2404694,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T01:55:49.000Z","msg":"一國一制<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f807c1723261d82ebe3c58fede601627c013a33","tid":2404694,"uid":152476,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T01:57:09.000Z","msg":"RTXG <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d5dba2deb4e965c0131a0ceb66f9f99ee21f5a1","tid":2404694,"uid":108146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26022c5e5b6db48f06df461a5fc9979960040b2c","tid":2404694,"uid":20262,"like":54,"dislike":2,"score":52,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T01:27:06.000Z","msg":"咁係咪代表可以解散廣管局"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-0